headline.main: Europe; Britain Would Strip Balkans of Crops Wanted by Reich

lead_paragraph: LONDON, March 31--As a result of the decision taken last week by the Supreme War Council one of the few new names and new faces in Great Britain's war Cabinet becomes a key man in the Allied offensive.
